name: Fritzfon solarimage
info:
#  Data input (need to be "http in" (Get) node originated)
 - msg.info as string or number (if not provided clock will be shown)
 - msg.house as string or number (if not provided will get calculated)
 - msg.toHouse as string or number (if not provided will get calculated)
 - msg.solar as string or number
 - msg.fromGrid as string or number
 - msg.toGrid as string or number

 # Following only works with numbers:
 #  Unit input
 ## Override "Input unit" per data
 - msg.houseUnit
 - msg.toHouseUnit
 - msg.solarUnit
 - msg.fromGridUnit
 - msg.toGridUnit

# Rounding
## Round modes:
Round = no unnecessary zeros.  
To fixed = add zeros to fit selected decemals.  

# Will Calculate house if not provided
house = msg.solar + msg.fromGrid - msg.toGrid.  
msg.toGrid is optional.

# Will Calculate toHouse if not provided
toHouse = msg.solar - msg.toGrid;

# kWh to €
## If only msg.solar provided
solar = solar * Grid cost
## Else
house = 
fromGrid * Grid cost * -1 + toGrid* Grid payment

solar = (solar - toGrid) * Grid cost + toGrid * Grid payment

fromGrid = fromGrid * Grid cost * -1

toGrid = toGrid * Grid payment

meta.desc: Show your current (solar) power information on your Fritzfon
